msgstr "Yes"

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:114
msgid "Configuració"
msgstr "Settings"

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:121
msgid "Site principal"
msgstr "Main site"

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:130
msgid ""
"El site del qual es llegeix la configuració de Vigilante. Per defecte, el "
"principal de la xarxa (normalment #1)."
msgstr ""
"The site whose Vigilante configuration is read. Defaults to the network's "
"main site (usually #1)."

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:134
msgid "Sincronització"
msgstr "Synchronization"

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:138
msgid "Copiar també el slug de custom-login al destí"
msgstr "Also copy the custom-login slug to the target"

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:142
msgid "Copiar també les llistes d'IPs (whitelist/blacklist)"
msgstr "Also copy the IP lists (whitelist/blacklist)"

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:146
msgid ""
"Copiar també la configuració de 2FA (només recomanat si el mètode és e-mail)"
msgstr ""
"Also copy the 2FA configuration (only recommended if the method is e-mail)"

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:148
msgid ""
"Per defecte es preserven les llistes d'IPs, la CSP report-uri i la "
"configuració de 2FA de cada site (camps específics per site). Atenció: amb "
"el mètode TOTP, els secrets viuen en taules per-blog i no es poden "
"sincronitzar; copiar la config de 2FA deixaria els usuaris sense poder "
"validar al destí."
msgstr ""
"By default the IP lists, the CSP report-uri and each site's 2FA "
"configuration are preserved (site-specific fields). Warning: with the TOTP "
"method, secrets live in per-blog tables and cannot be synchronized; copying "
"the 2FA config would leave users unable to validate on the target."

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:153
msgid "Login unificat"
msgstr "Unified login"

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:157
msgid ""
"Bloquejar el login als subsites (el login només es fa al site principal)"
msgstr "Block login on subsites (login is only performed on the main site)"

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:160
msgid ""
"Deshabilitat: la xarxa és de subdominis i la cookie d'autenticació no es "
"comparteix; el bloqueig et deixaria fora dels wp-admin dels subsites."
msgstr ""
"Disabled: this is a subdomain network and the authentication cookie is not "
"shared; blocking would lock you out of the subsites' wp-admin."

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:162
msgid ""
"Deshabilitat: cal que el site principal tingui el custom-login de Vigilante "
"configurat."
msgstr "Disabled: the main site must have Vigilante's custom-login configured."

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:164
msgid ""
"Els subsites respondran un 404 a qualsevol intent de login (wp-login.php i "
"slug), sense revelar el slug del principal. Inicia sessió un sol cop al "
"principal; la cookie de xarxa et dona accés a tots els subsites."
msgstr ""
"Subsites will return a 404 to any login attempt (wp-login.php and slug), "
"without revealing the main site's slug. Log in once on the main site; the "
"network cookie gives you access to all subsites."

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:169
msgid "Email d'avisos"
msgstr "Notification email"

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:172
msgid "Rebrà un avís quan Vigilante canviï de versió (un cop per versió)."
msgstr ""
"Will receive a notice when Vigilante changes version (once per version)."

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:177
msgid "Desar configuració"
msgstr "Save settings"

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:181
msgid "Sincronitzar ara"
msgstr "Sync now"

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:185
msgid ""
"Replica la configuració del site principal a la resta de sites de la xarxa."
msgstr ""
"Replicates the main site's configuration to the rest of the network's sites."

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:186
msgid "Sincronitza ara"
msgstr "Sync now"

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:190
msgid "Resultat de la sincronització"
msgstr "Synchronization result"

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:194
msgid "Site"
msgstr "Site"

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:196
msgid "Detall"
msgstr "Details"

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:207
msgid "Correcte"
msgstr "OK"

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:208
msgid "Sense canvis"
msgstr "No changes"

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:209
msgid "Error"
msgstr "Error"

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:222
msgid "Compatibilitat amb Vigilante"
msgstr "Vigilante compatibility"

#. translators: 1: versió validada, 2: versió coneguda
#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:227
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Versió de Vigilante validada per aquesta release: %1$s. Última versió "
"marcada com a compatible: %2$s."
msgstr ""
"Vigilante version validated by this release: %1$s. Last version marked as "
"compatible: %2$s."

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:236
msgid "He revisat: marca la versió actual com a compatible"
msgstr "I've reviewed it: mark the current version as compatible"

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:240
msgid "Recomanacions"
msgstr "Recommendations"

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:242
msgid "Mode bloqueig (recomanat per a 2FA un sol cop, xarxa multi-idioma):"
msgstr "Block mode (recommended for single 2FA, multilingual network):"

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:243
msgid ""
"configura el custom-login al site principal, mantén el slug copiat als "
"subsites (sync) i activa el bloqueig de login. El login només funciona al "
"principal; els subsites responen 404 sense revelar el slug. El 2FA s'enrola "
"un sol cop al principal i la cookie de xarxa cobreix la resta."
msgstr ""
"configure the custom-login on the main site, keep the slug copied to the "
"subsites (sync) and enable login blocking. Login only works on the main "
"site; subsites return 404 without revealing the slug. 2FA is set up once on "
"the main site and the network cookie covers the rest."

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:244
msgid "Mode independent:"
msgstr "Independent mode:"

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:245
msgid ""
"mateix slug a tots els sites (via sync) i bloqueig desactivat. Cada site "
"amaga el seu propi login; el 2FA s'enrola per-site (recorda: amb TOTP, no "
"sincronitzis la config de 2FA)."
msgstr ""
"same slug on all sites (via sync) and blocking disabled. Each site hides its "
"own login; 2FA is set up per-site (remember: with TOTP, do not synchronize "
"the 2FA config)."

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:246
msgid "Recuperació d'emergència:"
msgstr "Emergency recovery:"

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:247
msgid ""
"defineix VIGSYNC_DISABLE_LOGIN_GUARD a true al wp-config.php per desactivar "
"el bloqueig sense tocar la base de dades (també s'accepta l'antic "
"VIGSYNC_DISABLE_REDIRECT). El site principal mai es bloqueja."
msgstr ""
"define VIGSYNC_DISABLE_LOGIN_GUARD to true in wp-config.php to disable "
"blocking without touching the database (the legacy VIGSYNC_DISABLE_REDIRECT "
"is also accepted). The main site is never blocked."

#: vigilante-network-sync.php:69
msgid ""
"Vigilante Network Sync requereix una instal·lació WordPress multisite. "
"Desactiva el plugin."
msgstr ""
"Vigilante Network Sync requires a WordPress multisite installation. "
"Deactivate the plugin."
